Edna's good.

564
00:25:13.638 --> 00:25:15.306
We're close.

565
00:25:15.473 --> 00:25:17.308
All right. Kim. Edna's close.

566
00:25:17.434 --> 00:25:19.144
Are you OK?
Are you OK to keep going?

567
00:25:19.227 --> 00:25:20.729
