dropped her off?

681
00:29:44.826 --> 00:29:46.203
Or did he see her at 7:00.
have sex.

682
00:29:46.286 --> 00:29:48.371
and then
never see her after that?

683
00:29:48.538 --> 00:29:51.624
Well. we just need more.

684
00:29:51.791 --> 00:29:53.168
We need evidence
of what happened

685
00:29:53.251 --> 00:29:57.505
