00:30:56.106 --> 00:30:57.691
[recorder clicks]

704
00:30:57.816 --> 00:31:00.527
I've been thinking about
the people closest to me.

705
00:31:00.610 --> 00:31:02.154
Who have been there
for most of my firsts.

706
00:31:02.237 --> 00:31:03.947
