723
00:31:44.237 --> 00:31:46.740
Going to be a long shot.

724
00:31:46.906 --> 00:31:48.783
What if she was looking
at someone?

725
00:31:48.950 --> 00:31:51.578
Like someone who had
come to see her?

726
00:31:51.703 --> 00:31:54.831
